WEBVTT

00:05:58.427 --> 00:06:01.514
We just finished this 19-country study,
looking at that question.

00:06:01.538 --> 00:06:04.783
And around the world,
that's not a big number.

00:06:04.807 --> 00:06:06.607
In China, it's six percent.

00:06:08.608 --> 00:06:12.260
AG: An experiment from India demonstrates
the power of giving people a chance

00:06:12.284 --> 00:06:14.537
to use their strengths from day one.

00:06:14.561 --> 00:06:17.102
Some new hires in a call center
were randomly assigned

00:06:17.126 --> 00:06:19.282
to reflect on their individual strengths.

00:06:19.718 --> 00:06:22.472
They wrote about their
personal highlight reel,

00:06:22.496 --> 00:06:24.488
the moments they were at their best,

00:06:24.512 --> 00:06:27.329
and discussed how they could
bring those strengths to work.

00:06:28.147 --> 00:06:31.394
Six months later, they had
significantly higher performance,